                Imitatori invicti patris <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">Flavio Iulio Constant</supplied>i</del> <lb n="3"/>victori ac triumfatori <lb n="4"/>semper Augusto <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Celsinus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> urbi <lb n="6"/>iudex <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cogn</abbr><ex>itionum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>evotus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umini</ex></expan> m<expan><ex>aiestati</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> eius </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Turcius <lb n="2"/>Apronius <lb n="3"/>praefectus urbi <lb n="4"/>curavit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Statuenbasis auf der Rückseite mit einer späteren Inschrift (nach dem Doppelstrich) versehen: 362-364 n. Chr. (B): Ciancio Rossetto: Z. 3: triunfatori.</p>
            </div>
